data.description: Welcome to 235 South Sterley St.! This charming semi-detached home boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms, offering comfort and space for you and your family. Enjoy lazy afternoons on the inviting front porch, perfect for sipping lemonade or chatting with neighbors. Conveniently located off Route 222, commuting is a breeze, and both on and off-street parking ensure you always have a spot waiting for you. Why rent when you can own this affordable piece of paradise? Don't miss your chance to make this house your home!
